Do not attempt to release non-allocated face MBR

Fixes crash in _RegisterMissingFaces internal function
Closes #5684

Revert "Always initialize the mbr member of fetched faces"

This reverts commit 56023cc5b8fc6bb2f2a57483635e800c6c5eb446.

Closes #5707
Reopens #5684

Fix regression issue on 32-bit
and arm failures
References #5704 for PostGIS 3.5.0
Add invalidities check for #3280
Show all disabled tests on failure, not just first failing dir

Fix check for enabled tests

References #5704 in master branch (3.5.0dev)

Enable accidentally disabled tests

These are:

  - regress/core/geography_centroid
  - regress/core/geography_covers
  - topology/test/regress/validatetopologyrelation.sql

References #5704 in master branch (3.5.0dev)

Make geography_centroid tests tolerant to subtle differences

Check up to 10 decimal digits in text form

The test otherwise fails with 3.13.0dev-CAPI-1.18.0
but was not running in CI

References #5704 in master branch (3.5.0dev)

Fix geography_covers test syntax

It was broken by 51ff306d3f32217d00e9511cfe9463ddb0523adb
but the test was not running in CI

References #5704 in master branch (3.5.0dev)
Fix spurious number in debug line

Have _lwt_CheckEdgeCrossing check for interior-boundary intersections

So far only interior-interior intersections have been checked by
the function, missing an important kind of invalid edge addition.

References #5699

Allow debugging geoms in WKB format

Define POSTGIS_DEBUG_GEOMETRY_WKB to get HEXKWB instead of EWKT
Add more debugging lines

Simplify edge crossing validation by using boundary node rule

Boundary node rule is available in GEOS since 3.3 while
we require 3.8 or higher.

Translated PostGIS Manual using Weblate (Japanese)

Currently translated at 100.0% (5707 of 5707 strings)
